snippet: "The world has not yet forgotten World War II, but Russia is already keen on starting World War III." — Arseniy Yatsenyuk, Ukraine's acting prime minister, as top officials in Kiev spoke of imminent invasion from Russia....
lead_paragraph: "The world has not yet forgotten World War II, but Russia is already keen on starting World War III." — Arseniy Yatsenyuk, Ukraine's acting prime minister, as top officials in Kiev spoke of imminent invasion from Russia.
